{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Tingkah Kero-chan yang Bikin Susah Move On dari Anime Cardcaptor Sakura","content":"<p>Fans <a href=\"http://ccsakura-official.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cardcaptor Sakura</a> pasti masih inget sama Kero. Makhluk imut berwarna kuning yang memiliki sayap di punggungnya ini selalu ada dalam keseharian Kinomoto Sakura. Dalam artikel kali ini, CIAYO Blog bakal ngebahas tingkah-tingkah Kero yang bikin bro sis susah <em>move on </em>dari anime karya CLAMP ini.</p>\n<p>Sakura memanggil Cerberus dengan panggilan singkat Kero-chan. Meski tampilannya imut dan menggemaskan, wujud sebenarnya berupa singa bertubuh besar, bersayap putih-lebar.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23682\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23682\" data-attachment-id=\"23682\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/attachment/isi-2-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Twitter @ccsakura_info)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23682\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-23682\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Twitter @ccsakura_info)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat sedang berwujud singa, ia dilengkapi dengan pelindung dada dan helm tangguh bertahtakan batu berharga berwarna merah. Kero adalah makhluk penjaga buku yang menyegel kartu Clow. Kero lah yang memberikan kunci berwujud tongkat kepada Sakura untuk menyegel kartu Clow yang terlepas.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23688\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23688\" data-attachment-id=\"23688\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/attachment/isi-3-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Twitter @ccsakura_info)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23688\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3-2.jpg\" alt=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-23688\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Twitter @ccsakura_info)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kero yang imut tidak selalu bertingkah manis, kadang kelakuannya membuat Sakura kewalahan, bahkan sempat juga dibuat marah besar olehnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23697\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23697\" data-attachment-id=\"23697\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/attachment/isi-4-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Twitter @ccsakura_info)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23697\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4-3.jpg\" alt=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-23697\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Twitter @ccsakura_info)</p></div></p>\n<p>Ingat salah satu episode yang mengisahkan pertengkaran besar Kero dan Sakura? Kero yang keras kepala dan tidak mau kalah akhirnya minggat dari rumah.</p>\n<p>Ketidakhadiran Kero di rumah membuat Sakura cemas dan khawatir akan keberadaannya. Tapi setelah Kero mengirimkan fax dan mengatakan bahwa ia baik-baik saja, Sakura menjadi tenang. Saat sudah bertemu, Sakura menyiapkan kamar untuk Kero di dalam salah satu lacinya. Kamar Kero itu lengkap dengan tempat tidur, lemari, bantal, dan meja. Tentu saja semuanya dengan ukuran mungil.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23703\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23703\" data-attachment-id=\"23703\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/attachment/isi-6-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Youtube Sakura and Kero’s Big Fight)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Youtube Sakura and Kero’s Big Fight)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23703\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-3.jpg\" alt=\"(Youtube Sakura and Kero’s Big Fight)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-23703\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Youtube Sakura and Kero’s Big Fight)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hubungan pertemanan yang manis dan dibumbui dengan pertengkaran-pertengkaran kecil ini bisa bikin bro sis mewek terharu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23700\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23700\" data-attachment-id=\"23700\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/attachment/isi-5-25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Twitter @ccsakura_info)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23700\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5-3.jpg\" alt=\"(Twitter @ccsakura_info)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-23700\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Twitter @ccsakura_info)</p></div></p>\n<p>Wujud kecil bukan berarti suka diet. Kenyataannya, Kero ini makannya banyak. Bahkan bisa dikategorikan rakus. Selain cemilan-cemilan manis, keripik dan es serut, Kero juga pernah menghabiskan cokelat yang mengandung alkohol sendirian. Hahaha…keleyengan deh tuh dia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_23706\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-23706\" data-attachment-id=\"23706\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tingkah-kero-chan-yang-bikin-susah-move-dari-anime-cardcaptor-sakura/attachment/isi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(zerochan.net)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(zerochan.net)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23706\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI.jpg\" alt=\"(zerochan.net)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-23706\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(zerochan.net)</p></div></p>\n<p>Meski <em>bossy, </em>banyak mau, dan kadang ngeselin, Kero sangat peduli dengan Sakura dan yakin bahwa Sakura akan menjadi Clow Master selanjutnya. Ia juga mengawal Sakura mengumpulkan kartu-kartu. Gimana bro sis, makin kangen ya sama tingkah imut Kero-chan?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"703787b6-7680-5241-a4e8-f49a0f04be08"}}}